      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about \"growing and changing\" though. it's deeper than that. it's like the substance of who i was—the hope, the drive, the actual spark—it's just gone. extinguished. i feel like i'm just a shell performing the motions of a life that doesn't belong to me anymore. what's the point of all this \"growth\" if there's nothing left inside to actually experience it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
